spec_data.Name: python-turbokid
spec_data.Description:
This package provides a template engine plugin, allowing you
to easily use Kid with TurboGears, Buffet or other systems
that support python.templating.engines.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 29 Jul 2017 04:43:03 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Python template plugin that supports Kid templates
